Tag writer is peripheral that allows to read and write tag contents.

Available methods:
bool hasTag() - does peripheral contain valid tag?
string,int contents() - return current tag contents
bool,int write(string new_contents) - writes data to tag
string,int size() - return current tag size as (size_description, size_in_bytes) pair 
bool eject() - eject current tag

Peripheral will emit event ("tag",side) once tag is inserted 